Located in the prestigious York Cove this gorgeous apartment with water views is sure to take anyone's breath away from the moment you step into this property.  
 
This spacious home has a large modern kitchen with large modern European appliances including a dishwasher. Bench space is a key feature of this home and the abundance of cupboard space is sure to please the chef in the family.
